		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Wikipedia's stuff with &quot;reliable resources&quot; never made any sense.  Most of the sources on Wikipedia, have some kind of circular chain of citations, eventually looping back to Wikipedia.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


